NK015(ba)016:0: khro bo'i sems lnga bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)016:1: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK015(ba)016:2: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK015(ba)016:3: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK015(ba)016:4: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK015(ba)016:5: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)016:6: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)016:7: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK015(ba)016:8: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK015(ba)016:9: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)016:10: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK015(ba)016:14: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)016:15: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)016:16: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK015(ba)016:17: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK015(ba)016:18: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)016:19: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)016:20: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK015(ba)016:21: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK015(ba)016:22: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)016:23: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK015(ba)016:29: / 'das pa'i dus nas sngon byung ting 'dzin rnam gsum ltar bsgom rgyu'i yi ge h'u gsal ba las /
NK015(ba)016:30: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis tshur du brjod par bsam /
NK015(ba)016:32: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK015(ba)016:33: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab las /
NK015(ba)016:35: / 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ste //
NK015(ba)016:36: de tshe sems can thams cad la //
NK015(ba)016:37: shin tu khros shing gdug par 'gyur //
NK015(ba)016:38: shin tu khros dag gdug pa las //
NK015(ba)016:39: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK015(ba)016:40: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo las //
NK015(ba)016:41: khro bo de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK015(ba)016:42: sangs rgyas thugs rjes khros pas ni //
NK015(ba)016:43: thams cad 'jigs pa'i mchog yin te //
NK015(ba)016:44: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK015(ba)016:45: dam tshig las dang rnam sbyangs phyir //
NK015(ba)016:46: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK015(ba)016:47: b+h+r+aum gis gzhal yas khang bsgom /
NK015(ba)016:51: phata kyis sgo ma bzhi bsgom zhing khros par bsgul /
NK015(ba)016:52: b+h+yos dbang phyug ma rnams bskyed /
NK015(ba)016:53: b+h+r+aum h'u ha he phata b+h+yoh dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru kahm h+aa badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:62: bskyed pa dang 'dra ba gcig chos kyi sku las
NK015(ba)016:63: gzugs kyi skur bzhengs nas byon ma rag par bsgom
NK015(ba)016:67: ye shes can gyi spyod yul ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK015(ba)016:68: dal de gzhal yas khang gi shar du bsam mo
NK015(ba)016:71: sems can don slad dam tshig dgongs //
NK015(ba)016:72: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:73: e h+ya spyan drangs pa mdzes pa'i mu tra /
NK015(ba)016:75: dzahmh'u bam ting nge 'dzin dal de gzhal yas khang gi shar phyogs su bzhugs par bsam /
NK015(ba)016:78: dzahmh'u bam hoh tri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya ho /
NK015(ba)016:81: sh+r+ai he ru ka e h+ya hi hri sh+ya ho /
NK015(ba)016:86: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK015(ba)016:87: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs he ru kah chos sku zhi ba'i ngang las kyang //
NK015(ba)016:88: gzugs sku 'jigs tshul bstan du gsol //
NK015(ba)016:89: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pas //
NK015(ba)016:90: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:91: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal dang ldan //
NK015(ba)016:92: tshogs kyi slob dpon gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:93: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK015(ba)016:94: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs dang gshegs //
NK015(ba)016:95: sh+r+ai he ru kahm h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu tra pra be sha ya /
NK015(ba)016:98: sh+r+ai he ru kah ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:100: sa ma ya pra we sha ya h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:103: / 'gro ba ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)016:104: don gyi dbang du dgongs nas kyang /
NK015(ba)016:107: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya mu tra pra bany+dza mu tra h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:108: k+aa ya wak+ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:109: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK015(ba)016:110: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:111: mi gnyis don phyir mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK015(ba)016:112: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:113: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam /
NK015(ba)016:115: dam tshig brten pa'i phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)016:116: ye shes dam tshig brten par bya ba ni dbang du blang kar bcad par bcug /
NK015(ba)016:119: che mchog mnyam sbyor rol pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK015(ba)016:120: gdug pa 'dul mdzad khro bo'i skur ston pa //
NK015(ba)016:121: gsang sngags rmad byung drag po'i phrin las rnams //
NK015(ba)016:122: lhun gyis grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK015(ba)016:123: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK015(ba)016:124: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya ho /
NK015(ba)016:125: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya phata /
NK015(ba)016:126: dam tshig pa la gshegs pa yi //
NK015(ba)016:128: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs sam //
NK015(ba)016:129: grub pa mchog dag ma stsal na //
NK015(ba)016:131: dzahmh'u bam las kyi mkha' 'gro mas gdug pa bsgral ba mche ba'i phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)016:133: sh+r+ai he ru kah ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:136: ma ra si na pra bany+dza tsakra /
NK015(ba)016:141: he b+ha ga wan b+hud+d+ha k+she tra pra ti s+t+wam b+ha ga h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:142: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK015(ba)016:143: pho brang dkyil 'khor rang las sprul //
NK015(ba)016:144: nga ni bdud kyi bdud bdag ste //
NK015(ba)016:146: sh+r+ai badz+ra shar na dkar mo rgyas 'debs ma g.yon
NK015(ba)016:147: tshangs pa'i mgo g.yas mda' lnga ba rnams pa'i phyag
NK015(ba)016:148: rgya'o // mud ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya
NK015(ba)016:149: ya na mah lho na rmongs byed ma ser mos
NK015(ba)016:150: g.yon b+han+d+ha sbrang char gyis bkang ba g.yas gri khug
NK015(ba)016:152: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra ya ya na
NK015(ba)016:153: mah sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la ya
NK015(ba)016:154: nub na za ba mo dmar mos g.yas kha t+w+aam
NK015(ba)016:155: g.yon gri gug bsnams pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)016:156: ya na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya
NK015(ba)016:157: ya na mah byang nas tshe 'phel ma ljang ku
NK015(ba)016:158: g.yas na b+han+d+ha bdud rtsi lngas bkang ba'i kha rdo
NK015(ba)016:159: rje rgya gram gyis bcad pa la /
NK015(ba)016:160: sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku lte yan chad byung ba /
NK015(ba)016:161: g.yon dril bu bsnams pa'i phyag rgya bya'o //
NK015(ba)016:164: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+han+d+ha nam k+aa ro ya mi /
NK015(ba)016:165: ma h+aa g+ho ru a d+hi pa ti /
NK015(ba)016:168: bdag med don dam phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK015(ba)016:169: byams dang snying rje dgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK015(ba)016:170: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i /
NK015(ba)016:172: / 'jigs byed he ru kahl phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)016:173: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing /
NK015(ba)016:175: / 'dod dgur sgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK015(ba)016:176: shes rab rnam grol thugs rje'i ngang 'joms ma //
NK015(ba)016:177: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK015(ba)016:178: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)016:179: dbus kyi khrag 'thung phyag rgya ni //
NK015(ba)016:180: sku ni smug nag chen po la //
NK015(ba)016:181: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bsgrad //
NK015(ba)016:182: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus smug zhal //
NK015(ba)016:183: rdo rje khor yug ral gri g.yas //
NK015(ba)016:184: b+han+d+ha dgra s+t+wa gshol shing g.yon //
NK015(ba)016:186: sangs rgyas khros pa'i rgyal mo che //
NK015(ba)016:187: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi ldan zhing //
NK015(ba)016:188: kem rus 'bum gyis sku la brgyan //
NK015(ba)016:190: g.yas pas thabs kyi gtso la 'khyud //
NK015(ba)016:192: zla gam ljags kyi mchod pa yis //
NK015(ba)016:194: se gol sgra yi mchod pa yi //
NK015(ba)016:195: sangs rgyas thams cad sdud par mdzad //
NK015(ba)016:196: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:197: b+hud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK015(ba)016:198: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:200: shar phyogs khrag 'thung phyag rgya ni //
NK015(ba)016:201: sku ni sngo nag chen po la //
NK015(ba)016:202: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bsgrad //
NK015(ba)016:203: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK015(ba)016:204: rdo rje 'khor yug ral gri g.yas //
NK015(ba)016:205: b+han d+ha dgra s+t+wa gshol shing g.yon //
NK015(ba)016:206: de yi yum chen 'jigs byed ma //
NK015(ba)016:207: rdo rje khros pa'i rgyal mo ste //
NK015(ba)016:208: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi ldan ma //
NK015(ba)016:209: kem rus 'bum gyis sku la brgyan //

NK015(ba)016:281: karma kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK015(ba)016:282: karma kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:284: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK015(ba)016:285: koo r+ai b+han dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK015(ba)016:286: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:288: coo r+ai mda' gzhu 'geng ma ser //
NK015(ba)016:290: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK015(ba)016:292: be t+aa byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK015(ba)016:298: sme sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK015(ba)016:302: sing+ha kha ro bsnol ser sing //
NK015(ba)016:303: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:305: b+ha g+h+ri gnas blta bsnol dmar stag /
NK015(ba)016:306: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+aa he /
NK015(ba)016:307: sri la nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK015(ba)016:308: badz+ra sing+ha la mu kh+aa he /
NK015(ba)016:309: shwa na 'dral lha mthing nag spyang //
NK015(ba)016:310: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+aa he /
NK015(ba)016:311: kri ta mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK015(ba)016:313: kang+ka zhing phrag bsnol mgo reng //
NK015(ba)016:315: kha kh+aa bya ro b+han gri nag /
NK015(ba)016:316: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+aa he /
NK015(ba)016:317: hu lu rdor dbyug sna tshogs 'ug /
NK015(ba)016:318: badz+ra u l+au ka mu kh+aa he /
NK015(ba)016:319: rta gdong mthing ga lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:320: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:321: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza //
NK015(ba)016:322: phag gdong ser mo mche zhags 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:324: nyi zla lcags sgrog me 'bar ma //
NK015(ba)016:326: thal byed dril bu sna tshogs mdog /
NK015(ba)016:327: badz+ra b+ha smi ba la ba tu hoh b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:328: shar gyi ma drug dbang phyug ma //
NK015(ba)016:329: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK015(ba)016:330: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:334: lha chen dkar ljang tri shul /
NK015(ba)016:338: gzhon nu dmar mos mdung thung 'phen //
NK015(ba)016:340: brgya byin dkar mos in+d+ra gdeng //
NK015(ba)016:343: lho'i ma drug dbang phyug ma //
NK015(ba)016:345: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:349: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK015(ba)016:351: be con ljang nag thod dbyug 'phyar //
NK015(ba)016:353: srin mo dmar ser dung khrag 'thung //
NK015(ba)016:355: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK015(ba)016:358: nub kyi ma drug dbang phyug ma //
NK015(ba)016:359: dga' ba dmar mos ga dar 'chang //
NK015(ba)016:360: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:362: stobs chen dkar mos gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:363: re tri re ma ti b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:364: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK015(ba)016:365: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:367: ma nu ha ra ma b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:368: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:370: rlung lha sngo skya ba dan 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:374: byang gi ma drug dbang phyug ma //
NK015(ba)016:375: gsod byed nag mo ral gri so //
NK015(ba)016:376: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod par rol //
NK015(ba)016:377: ma h+aa ma r+aa n+aa b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:380: me mo dmar mos gsal shing 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:382: phag mo nag mos mche zhags 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:384: rgan byed nag mo zhing chung za //
NK015(ba)016:385: tsa mun tri b+h+yoh sna chen dkar ljang thod khrag 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:387: chu lha sngon pos sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:389: sgo bzhi ma chen dbang phyug ma //
NK015(ba)016:390: rdo rje mthing nag lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:391: badz+ra ma h+aa li la b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:392: rdo rje dmar ser ra mgo zhags //
NK015(ba)016:394: rdo rje bum rna lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK015(ba)016:395: badz+ra bum pa ka ra na b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:397: badz+ra lam+bo d+ha ra na b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:398: gnas yul ma mo nyi shu dang /
NK015(ba)016:400: ma bkral tshig bzhi re sprad /
NK015(ba)016:401: dbang phyug mal tshigs drug re dang /
NK015(ba)016:402: sngags drug sbyar ba yang yod /
NK015(ba)016:403: kun bzang gi mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)016:404: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)016:405: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi //
NK015(ba)016:406: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyi //
NK015(ba)016:407: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad byung kun //
NK015(ba)016:408: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK015(ba)016:409: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo b+hi shwa mu khe b+h+ya /
NK015(ba)016:411: sarba s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)016:421: sh+r+ai b+ha ga wan kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:423: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:429: sh+r+ai bam kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:430: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang /
NK015(ba)016:431: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK015(ba)016:432: dpal chen khrag 'thung 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK015(ba)016:433: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK015(ba)016:434: thod pa skam rlon mkha' ltar gtsigs //
NK015(ba)016:435: zhing chen gsar rnying sti rar bcas //
NK015(ba)016:436: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK015(ba)016:438: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:441: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK015(ba)016:444: ma ra ya kra ma kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:445: h+r+ai da ya pi pa h'u phata /
NK015(ba)016:446: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK015(ba)016:447: srid pa'i dra ba chags pa rnams //
NK015(ba)016:448: dmar chen po yi ar+g+ham la /
NK015(ba)016:451: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK015(ba)016:452: khams gsum ma lus bsgral bar byed //
NK015(ba)016:453: gdul dka' 'dul bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)016:454: sha rus la sogs za bar byed //
NK015(ba)016:462: ma h+aa ba su ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK015(ba)016:463: kha kha kha le le le h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)016:466: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK015(ba)016:467: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK015(ba)016:468: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga'i dngos //
NK015(ba)016:469: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK015(ba)016:470: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK015(ba)016:471: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK015(ba)016:472: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK015(ba)016:473: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK015(ba)016:474: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK015(ba)016:475: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //
NK015(ba)016:476: lha dang lha min gsang ba'i bdag /
NK015(ba)016:477: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK015(ba)016:478: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK015(ba)016:479: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK015(ba)016:480: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK015(ba)016:481: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK015(ba)016:482: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:483: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:484: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK015(ba)016:485: dpal chen badz+ra he ru dang /
NK015(ba)016:486: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri la /
NK015(ba)016:487: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:488: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:489: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:490: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:491: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa dpal chen b+hud+d+ha he ru dang /
NK015(ba)016:492: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri la /
NK015(ba)016:493: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:494: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:495: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:496: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:497: na mahsarba dpal chen rat+na he ru dang //
NK015(ba)016:498: rat+na kro ti shwa ri la //
NK015(ba)016:499: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:500: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:501: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:502: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:503: na mahsarba dpal chen pad+ma he ru dang //
NK015(ba)016:504: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri la //
NK015(ba)016:505: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:506: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:507: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:508: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:509: na mahsarba dpal chen b+hi sha he ru dang //
NK015(ba)016:510: b+h+yi sha kro ti sha ri la //
NK015(ba)016:511: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:512: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:513: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:514: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:515: na mahsarba dpal chen mi pham rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)016:516: ma tshogs dbang phyug 'khor gyis brgyan //
NK015(ba)016:517: ko'u ri la sogs bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:518: tsan+d+ha la sogs bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:519: sing ha la sogs bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:520: kri ta la sogs bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:521: sgo ma chen mo bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:522: ma mo chen mo bdun rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:523: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams dang //
NK015(ba)016:525: bla med dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod //
NK015(ba)016:526: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:527: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK015(ba)016:528: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)016:529: sarba sh+r+ai ban kha hi kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:534: dgyes pas rdo rje gsor mdzad nas //
NK015(ba)016:535: byang chub sems sprin dbab tu gsol //
NK015(ba)016:536: rdo rje gsor ba'i dga' mchog 'di /
NK015(ba)016:540: rdo rje 'dzin ma ldan la byung //
NK015(ba)016:541: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi mkha' dbyings su //
NK015(ba)016:542: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus mchog dkod de //
NK015(ba)016:543: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i sbyor mchod kyis //
NK015(ba)016:544: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)016:547: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK015(ba)016:549: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta a la la ho /
NK015(ba)016:551: b+ha la b+han+d+ha bcud yangs pa'i /
NK015(ba)016:554: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)016:556: / 'jig byed bka' bzlog dgyes par mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:557: rdo rje rtse gsum 'bar ba'i sku gsung thugs //
NK015(ba)016:558: srid gsum rtse 'jom dri shu la //
NK015(ba)016:559: khams gsum rab tu dkrugs nas ni //
NK015(ba)016:560: za byed chen po'i zhal du ni /
NK015(ba)016:562: / 'gro kun skad cig yud la stab /
NK015(ba)016:565: za byed khyed lngas kun za nas //
NK015(ba)016:566: dngos por gyur pa'i bgegs 'di kun //
NK015(ba)016:567: ngas btab khyed kyis yud la rol //
NK015(ba)016:570: ye shes dbyings kyi rnga rdungs pas /
NK015(ba)016:572: / 'go min bla med gnas mchog nas /
NK015(ba)016:574: / 'das pa'i sangs rgyas spyan drangs te //
NK015(ba)016:576: byin gyis brlab cing gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:580: bsgrub pa las kyi rnga brdungs pas //
NK015(ba)016:581: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang //
NK015(ba)016:582: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK015(ba)016:583: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK015(ba)016:584: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog 'dir //
NK015(ba)016:585: byin gyis brlab phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:586: byin gyis brlab phyir gshegs nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:587: rmad du byung bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK015(ba)016:591: gsang ba yum gyi rnga brdungs pas //
NK015(ba)016:593: ma sring rgya mtsho 'khor bcas rnams //
NK015(ba)016:594: ci bder rol zhing gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:595: ci bdir rol zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:596: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:600: tshar gsum pa yi rnga brdungs pas //
NK015(ba)016:601: rdo rje srin po'i rnga sgra yis //
NK015(ba)016:602: ru tra nag po'i glad pa 'gem //
NK015(ba)016:603: dri shu la yi mdung rtse yis //
NK015(ba)016:605: ma sring rgya mtsho'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK015(ba)016:606: dgra bgegs gdug pa'i lnga phung 'joms //
NK015(ba)016:612: srid pa ngo bo nyid kyis bdag /
NK015(ba)016:613: rang bzhin du ni dngos med byos //
NK015(ba)016:614: rang bzhin dag pa'i sems can rnams //
NK015(ba)016:615: dag pa nyid ni rtogs par shog /
NK015(ba)016:619: g+han+d+he sgra yis grol bar mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:620: chos dbyings mnyam nyid rigs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK015(ba)016:621: mkha' la dus kyi dril bu'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK015(ba)016:622: dril bu'i sgra mthar stong pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK015(ba)016:623: rigs lnga khrag 'thung tshogs rnams mnyes gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:627: snang srid mnyam nyid brdal ba'i dbyings nyid las //
NK015(ba)016:628: mkha' la dus kyis dril bu'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK015(ba)016:629: dril bu'i sgra mthar stong pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK015(ba)016:630: dbyings phyug yum lnga'i thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:632: rnam dag yongs su bkong ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK015(ba)016:633: mkha' la dus kyi dril bu'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK015(ba)016:634: dril bu'i sgra mthar stong pa shes rab kyis //
NK015(ba)016:635: mkha' 'gro phra men tshogs rnams mnyes gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:637: dur khrod gnas mchog bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK015(ba)016:638: mkha' la dus kyi dril bu'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK015(ba)016:639: dril bu'i sgra mthar stong pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK015(ba)016:640: ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams mnyes gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:642: rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK015(ba)016:643: mkha' la dus kyi dril bu'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK015(ba)016:644: dril bu'i sgra mthar stong pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK015(ba)016:645: sgo ma bzhi'i tshogs rnams mnyes gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:647: gdal khyab chos dbyings mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK015(ba)016:648: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i sku mchog 'byung ba ni //
NK015(ba)016:649: la la tshangs pa stongs pas lhag par zhi //
NK015(ba)016:650: la la dus mtha'i me ltar rab tu 'bar //
NK015(ba)016:651: la la khyab 'jug stong bas lhag par grags //
NK015(ba)016:652: la la gshin rje stong pas lhag par rngam //
NK015(ba)016:653: la la dbang phyug stong pa lhag par 'dud /
NK015(ba)016:655: / 'jig rten khams ni stong dag nas //
NK015(ba)016:657: bde ba'i longs spyod rgyan du rol //
NK015(ba)016:658: gar dag byed cing rab tu zo //
NK015(ba)016:659: sil sil ma ma sing sing //
NK015(ba)016:664: rnal 'byor bde mchog sgyu mar sprul //
NK015(ba)016:665: dam tshig dag la 'jug tu gsol //
NK015(ba)016:666: nyon mongs dag la rgyal bar mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:667: ma lus pa dag bsnams su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:668: nyon mongs thams cad bsal bar mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:669: rnam pa sna tshogs 'dod chags rgyud kyi sems can ma lus lus pa med pa 'dul mkhas pas /
NK015(ba)016:670: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma mkha' gro
NK015(ba)016:671: bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab sprul rnam par
NK015(ba)016:672: sprul // te na te te h'u /
NK015(ba)016:673: rnam pa sna tshogs rab tu dga' ba'i rgyud kyi
NK015(ba)016:674: sems can ma lus lus pa med pa 'dul mkhas
NK015(ba)016:675: pa / de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma
NK015(ba)016:676: bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab sprul rnam par
NK015(ba)016:678: rnam pa sna tshogs khro bo'i rgyud kyi sems can ma lus lus pa med pa 'dul mkhas pa /
NK015(ba)016:679: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab sprul rnam par sprul /
NK015(ba)016:680: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK015(ba)016:681: rnam pa sna tshogs srog gi rgyud kyis sems can ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas pas /
NK015(ba)016:682: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab sprul rnam par sprul /
NK015(ba)016:683: h'u shi sha bi sha h'u /
NK015(ba)016:686: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar /
NK015(ba)016:689: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK015(ba)016:690: mche ba zang yag za byed che ho /
NK015(ba)016:692: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK015(ba)016:693: thug chom ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK015(ba)016:694: a la ha la'i gad rgyang che //
NK015(ba)016:695: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che ho /
NK015(ba)016:697: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK015(ba)016:698: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal /
NK015(ba)016:701: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che ho /
NK015(ba)016:703: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK015(ba)016:706: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che ho /
NK015(ba)016:708: bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po //
NK015(ba)016:709: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms /
NK015(ba)016:713: / 'jigs byed chen po thig le che'o //
NK015(ba)016:715: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK015(ba)016:716: rdo rje chu bo sdud po che //
NK015(ba)016:717: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK015(ba)016:718: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho //
NK015(ba)016:719: de nas yi dam kun la rtsa sngags mthar kh+aa hi brjod /
NK015(ba)016:728: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams mnyes par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:729: dam can rgya mtsho thugs dam skongs bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:730: mchod pa rgya mtsho gnas su stobs par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:731: srid pa rgya mtsho dbyings su sgrol bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:732: dam tshig chag nyams skongs bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:733: bdud dpung rgya mtsho bcom par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:734: bgegs dpung rgya mtsho zhi bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:735: 'khor ba rgya mtsho stongs par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:736: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho zhi bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:737: bdag nyid chen po lhun gyi grub par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:738: bdag cag rnal 'byor pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)016:739: ces sogs smon lam btab bo //
NK015(ba)016:740: ma tshang ba kha bskang ba ni /
NK015(ba)016:747: sha sha sa ha k+shah a +aa /
NK015(ba)016:755: badz+ra sat+wa sa ma ya yi ge brgya pa tshang bar brjod /
NK015(ba)016:759: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba'am /
NK015(ba)016:760: rda dal thabs khu brdung la 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)016:761: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK015(ba)016:762: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)016:763: dpal chen he ru ka'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)016:764: thugs rje che mnga' rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)016:765: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK015(ba)016:766: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)016:767: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)016:768: ma sring rgya mtsho'i sku la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)016:769: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK015(ba)016:770: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)016:771: chos skyong srung ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)016:772: dam can rgya mtshos tshogs la gzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)016:773: gsang sngags rmad byung theg chen sgor zhugs rnal 'byor rnams //
NK015(ba)016:774: lta ba 'phang dam chos nyid don ma rtogs //
NK015(ba)016:775: bsgom pa yun thung yi dam lha ma 'dres //
NK015(ba)016:776: spyod pa rlab chung yi dam lha ma mnyes //
NK015(ba)016:777: sbyin pa stobs chung ser sna'i mdud ma grol //
NK015(ba)016:778: bsam gtan stobs chung 'dod chags sems ma non //
NK015(ba)016:779: snying rje shugs chung zhe sdang spro ma zhi //
NK015(ba)016:780: shes rab blo chung gti mug mun ma sel //
NK015(ba)016:781: ma mthong mthong gi lha 'drer bskur btab bam //
NK015(ba)016:782: ma nyes pa la sngags kyi zer thal lam //
NK015(ba)016:783: ma rtogs pa la phur bu'i dpal thal lam //
NK015(ba)016:784: sman med ar+g+hasa yi dam lha mchod dam //
NK015(ba)016:785: sta na byin gyis ma rlobs gnas 'khyams sam //
NK015(ba)016:786: g+ha na byin gyis ma rlobs ru la khyer ram /
NK015(ba)016:787: dkyil 'khor bri nor mar me 'bar bsad dam //
NK015(ba)016:788: phyi yi 'dul khrims ma srungs khrims nyams sam //
NK015(ba)016:789: nang gi dam tshig ma bsrungs dam nyams sam //
NK015(ba)016:790: bsrungs mtshams ma mchis sdig dang gral gcig gi //
NK015(ba)016:791: slob dpon bka' drin can gyi bka' bcag gam //
NK015(ba)016:792: grogs mched khyad par can gyi thugs dkrugs sam //
NK015(ba)016:793: dmag chen dpon byas ling chen kha bsgyur ram //
NK015(ba)016:794: chu bsgyung me bkyes sems can srog bcad dam //
NK015(ba)016:795: de la sogs te nyes sgrib ci mchis rnams /
NK015(ba)016:797: / 'phags pa mngon sum bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar 'dir //
NK015(ba)016:798: gnod 'gyod yid la dran te mthol zhing bshags //
NK015(ba)016:799: bdag cag sems can lags pas ma rig 'khrul par bgyi //
NK015(ba)016:800: sgyu ma lugs pas nongs pa rjes su bshags //
NK015(ba)016:801: thugs rje chen pos bzod pa dang du bzhes //
NK015(ba)016:802: ye shes chen pos tshangs pa stsal tu stsol //
NK015(ba)016:805: bzlas pa'i rjes su lhag ma'i las rgyan /
NK015(ba)016:807: spyan drangs shing dam la gzhugs pa dang /
NK015(ba)016:808: kha chus gang bcing mchod pa'i cho ga dang /
NK015(ba)016:809: las bcol cing mchod pa'i cho ga dang /
NK015(ba)016:810: las bcol zhing gshegs su gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)016:811: dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK015(ba)016:812: mdzes pa'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK015(ba)016:814: dzahmh'u bam hoh badz+ra d+aak+ka d+aak+ki ni tri sh+ya ho /
NK015(ba)016:818: zhes thal mo'i sgra lan gsum bya'o //
NK015(ba)016:819: de nas rnga chung brdung zhing spyugs glu blang ba 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)016:821: dam tshig brda'i mtshon nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:822: ma tshogs dbang phyug spyan 'dren gyis //
NK015(ba)016:823: dam bca' bzhin du da tshur byon //
NK015(ba)016:824: gsur chen brda'i mtshon nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:825: ma tshogs dbang phyug spyan 'dren gyis //
NK015(ba)016:826: dam bcas bzhin du da tshur byon //
NK015(ba)016:827: sbyugs pa brda'i mtshon nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:828: ma tshogs dbang phyug spyan 'dren gyis //
NK015(ba)016:829: dam bcas bzhin du da tshur byon /
NK015(ba)016:830: rnga chung brda'i mtshon nas kyang //
NK015(ba)016:831: ma tshogs dbang phyug spyan 'dren gyis //
NK015(ba)016:832: dam bcas bzhin du da tshur byon //
NK015(ba)016:833: de nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK015(ba)016:835: ta ki r+aa tsa h'u dzah ta ki r+aa tsa dzah a gats+tsha ya /
NK015(ba)016:849: sarba badz+ra da ki ni nam /
NK015(ba)016:853: ces pas rang gi gnas nas byon te /
NK015(ba)016:854: dkyil 'khor gyi rim du zhing tshal ba'i gdan la 'khod par bsam mo //
NK015(ba)016:855: rang rang gi dam tshig rjes su dran nas /
NK015(ba)016:856: srog gi snying po dpal chen po la phul ba'i tshul du bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)016:857: de nas bdag gi zhal nas /
NK015(ba)016:858: gtor ma la bdud rtsi'i zhal chab kyi char phab nas /
NK015(ba)016:859: ma mo rnams kyi ljags la thim par bsgom pa ni kha chu'i mchod pa'o //
NK015(ba)016:860: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor chen por dmigs te /
NK015(ba)016:861: ma mo rnams kyis gsol bar bsgom yang gtor ma
NK015(ba)016:862: dug gsum gyi rgya mtsho'i sha khrag rus par gyur
NK015(ba)016:863: te / ma mo rnams kyis gsol bar bsgom zhing /
NK015(ba)016:864: sarba badz+ra d+aak+ka d+aak+ki ni pra tits+tsha i mam b+ha ling+ta h'u phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:865: sarba b+hud+d+ha dak+ka d+aak+ki pra tits+tsha i mam b+ha ling+ta phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:866: sarba rat+na dak+ka d+aak+ki ni pra tits+tsha i mam b+ha ling+ta tram phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:867: h+r+aihsarba pad+ma dak+ka d+aak+ki ni pra tits+tsha i mam b+ha ling+ta h+r+aihphata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:868: ha sarba karma d+aak+ka d+aak+ka ni pra tits+tsha i mam b+ha ling+ta h+aa phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:869: ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:870: bra h+ma n+ai b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:871: re'u tri ma b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:872: b+ha na b+he b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:873: ku m+aa r+ai b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:874: in+d+ra ya ni b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:875: badz+ra sing+ha ka la b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:876: a mri tam b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:878: ta na ham b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:881: ra tri ma b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:882: re tri re ma ti b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:883: e ka tsha ra ma b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:884: ma nu ha ra ma b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:885: si ti kam b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:886: b+h+aa ya b+h+ae b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:887: ma h+aa m+aa ra n+aa b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:889: ba r+aa h+ai b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:890: tsa mun dri b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:891: pu ta na b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:892: p+aa ni badz+ra b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:893: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa l+ai b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:894: tsa k+aa la badz+ra b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:895: badz+ra bum pa ka ra na b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:896: badz+ra lam+bo d+ha ra na b+h+yo kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:897: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:898: ma h+aa k+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:899: ma h+aa tsit+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:900: ma h+aa ba su ta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:901: dgra bgegs kyi ming bzhi'i phung po kha kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:902: rnam shes tshogs brgyad la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:903: lhag ma'i rjes shul la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)016:905: de nas ma mo thams cad kyis bdag la bka'
NK015(ba)016:906: nyan pa'i tshul gyis las bsgrub pa'i nyer logs su
NK015(ba)016:910: mi srin mo dang tshangs ma dang /
NK015(ba)016:913: gzhon nu mo dang dbang mo dang //
NK015(ba)016:914: rdo rje dmar mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK015(ba)016:915: zhi ba mo dang be con mo //
NK015(ba)016:916: srin mo dang ni zab mo //
NK015(ba)016:917: rdo rje dga' ma chen mo dang //
NK015(ba)016:918: shin tu ra ro khrag 'thung myos //
NK015(ba)016:919: gcig pur spyod dang yid 'phrog mo //
NK015(ba)016:920: klu mo dang ni rlung me dang //
NK015(ba)016:921: rdo rje yang ni gsod chen mo //
NK015(ba)016:922: me mo phag mo rga na byed mo //
NK015(ba)016:923: sna chen mo dang chu lha mo //
NK015(ba)016:924: rdo rje nag mo chen mo dang //
NK015(ba)016:925: rdo rje ra ste dmar ser mo //
NK015(ba)016:926: rdo rje sngo nag bum rna mo //
NK015(ba)016:927: rdo rje nag mo gsus 'dzin te //
NK015(ba)016:928: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK015(ba)016:929: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK015(ba)016:930: spyan sngar khas blang dam bcas bzhin /
NK015(ba)016:933: ye shes thob par bya ba dang //
NK015(ba)016:934: bsgrub pa po'i grogs bya zhes //
NK015(ba)016:935: rdo rje byin nas ming btags te //
NK015(ba)016:936: dam bcas bzhin du he ru ka'i //
NK015(ba)016:939: / 'di tshe so so'i gzugs mchog dang //
NK015(ba)016:940: mngon par ston la grub par phul //
NK015(ba)016:941: khyed rnams mngon du ma gyur ram //
NK015(ba)016:942: grub pa mchog dag cha btsal na //
NK015(ba)016:943: so so'i thugs dang 'gal gyur pas //
NK015(ba)016:944: deng gi gnas mchog dam pa 'dir /
NK015(ba)016:946: / 'dus la las rnams kun byos shig /
NK015(ba)016:947: thabs chen zla gsang thig le las //
NK015(ba)016:948: g.yar dam can la brtser dgongs te /
NK015(ba)016:951: mdzes pa'i sku la gzhon sgeg tshul 'chang zhing //
NK015(ba)016:952: me tog chun 'phyangs legs pa'i sked chings can //
NK015(ba)016:953: dbang phyug chen po'i chung ma las mdzad da tshur byon //
NK015(ba)016:954: thugs dam bzhin du bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:955: dbang phyug chen po'i chung ma nyi shu brgyad //
NK015(ba)016:958: / 'dir gshegs bka'i gtor ma 'di long la //
NK015(ba)016:959: bdag cag rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:960: bdud dpung chom la bgegs dpung shig /
NK015(ba)016:961: bdud kyi zhags pa nag po chod //
NK015(ba)016:962: gshin rje'i khram kha dgra la bsgyur //
NK015(ba)016:963: yid la brnag pa'i dgra bgegs la //
NK015(ba)016:964: rtags phyung mtshan ma myur du ston //
NK015(ba)016:968: rang rang gi gnas su gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)016:969: de nas gtor ma gom pa bdun cu'i sar phyir bsnur la /
NK015(ba)016:970: gangs re'i rgyud la gnas pa'i brten ma rnams /
NK015(ba)016:971: lag tu rdo rje byin nas de nas ming gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK015(ba)016:973: bod khams skyongs pa'i ma mo'i tshogs //
NK015(ba)016:974: brten ma chen mo bcu gnyis kyang //
NK015(ba)016:975: sngon gyi thugs dam dgongs mdzod la /
NK015(ba)016:977: / 'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK015(ba)016:979: dgong sngon mthon po'i yar steng nas //
NK015(ba)016:980: nam mkha'i rgyal mo rdo rje ting lo sman //
NK015(ba)016:981: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK015(ba)016:982: ma btsun khug chos rdo rje dbyar mo bsil //
NK015(ba)016:983: rkong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK015(ba)016:984: lho'i skyi mthing rdo rje ya ma skyong //
NK015(ba)016:985: byang gi sman ting rdo rje ting mi btsun //
NK015(ba)016:986: btsan la rol pa'i rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK015(ba)016:987: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje g.yu bun ma //
NK015(ba)016:988: brda lha btsun mo rdo rje ye shes mchog /
NK015(ba)016:989: skyi mthing gangs kyi rdo rje la ro sman //
NK015(ba)016:990: yar 'brog gser thang rdo rje 'brog sring ma //
NK015(ba)016:991: khrag 'thung chen mo rdo rje g.yu sgron ma //
NK015(ba)016:992: mi g.yo brten pa'i rdo rjes 'dzin ma //
NK015(ba)016:993: gangs ri'i rgyud la gnas pa yi //
NK015(ba)016:994: brten ma chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK015(ba)016:995: bdud rtsi sman gyis g.yab 'dor nas /
NK015(ba)016:997: / 'dir gshegs bka'i gtor ma 'di long la //
NK015(ba)016:998: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)016:1000: rims nad yams nad bcad pa dang /
NK015(ba)016:1001: ci las gyur pa'i nad rnams kun //
NK015(ba)016:1002: yud tsam gyis ni med par mdzod //
